		<section class="my-20 lg:my-32">
			<h3 class="mb-14 text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-normal dark:text-white">
				We celebrate <span class="font-bold">unity</span> and <span class="font-bold">teamwork</span
				>!
			</h3>
			<p class="mb-16 text-lg lg:text-2xl dark:text-white">
				At Mango Business Center, we firmly believe that a positive work environment contributes to
				everyone's success. For this reason, we design a series of activities throughout the year to
				strengthen the ties between us and encourage an environment full of energy and partnership.
				Here you can see a gallery of unique moments in our quarterly activities, continuous
				training and other important moments for us.
			</p>
